      "theme": "Maps PowerPoint Office theme color slots to canonical token values. accent1 = highlight, accent2 = cookieDough, accent3 = burgendy, accent4 = cream, accent5 = wine, accent6 = habourMist, dk2 = plum, lt2 = ashGrey. Validated against the .pptx templates by scripts/validate-pptx.py."
